# Cloudflare Pages custom headers for the Eigen widget CDN origin.
#
# Applies to every path under the Pages project (eigen-d3x.pages.dev and
# any custom domains bound to it). Headers here are the outer hardening
# layer for an iframe that ships HMAC-signed widget tokens and streams
# SSE responses from Supabase.
#
# Notes:
# - Content-Security-Policy is deliberately strict: no third-party
#   scripts, no inline script/style allowed, only the widget's origin
#   for assets, and connect-src limited to the Supabase Functions host
#   that actually issues tokens and serves eigen-widget-chat. If we
#   ever move api_base to a different origin, update connect-src.
# - frame-ancestors is a wildcard because the widget is designed to be
#   embedded by any approved customer site; the real per-site origin
#   allowlist is enforced server-side by eigen-widget-session, which
#   rejects requests whose Origin header isn't in the registry. Do NOT
#   rely on frame-ancestors alone to gate embedding.
# - X-Frame-Options is intentionally omitted; modern browsers prefer
#   frame-ancestors from CSP, and mixing the two can break legitimate
#   embedders on older Safari.
# - HSTS is two-year, includeSubDomains, preload-ready. pages.dev is
#   already preloaded; this mirrors the directive on custom domains.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob:; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self' https://zudslxucibosjwefojtm.supabase.co; frame-ancestors *; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=(), payment=(), usb=(), accelerometer=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=()
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: unsafe-none
